Tabular tools for raster

Source: R/tabularaster-package.R
tabularaster.Rd

Extract and index with raster tidy tools for raster.

Details

Tabularaster includes these main functions.

as_tibbleconvert raster data to data frame form, with control over output and form of dimension/coordinate columns
cellnumbersextract a data frame of query identifiers and cell,pixel index numbers
decimatefast and loose resizing of a raster to coarser resolution
index_extentbuild an extent in row column form, as opposed to coordinate value form
